# 8. EXECUTION FLOW

## 8.1 Standard Flow

1. Select ticker
2. Fetch cached score
3. Display Compatibility Card
4. User action:

   * Deploy
   * Add to Watch
   * Override

---

## 8.2 Compatibility Card UI

Displays:

