---

# 9. OVERRIDE SYSTEM (CORE)

## 9.1 Trigger Condition

* Hard rule failure OR user override intent

---

## 9.2 Friction Flow

1. Warning message
2. 30-second timer
3. Justification input

---

## 9.3 Justification Validation

### Heuristic Validation

```
JustificationValidation {
  minWordCount: 8
  minUniqueWordRatio: 0.5
}
```

---

### AI Audit (Async)

* Classifies justification quality
* Flags low-effort entries

---

## 9.4 Override Classification

* Valid Override
* Low-Quality Override
* High-Risk Override (during drawdown)

---

## 9.5 Override Memory Injection

System displays past override outcomes before confirmation

---

