# 22. STATE MACHINES

## 22.1 Trade Lifecycle

States:

* INITIATED
* EVALUATED
* BLOCKED
* DEPLOYED
* OVERRIDDEN
* CLOSED

Transitions:
INITIATED → EVALUATED
EVALUATED → DEPLOYED (if valid)
EVALUATED → BLOCKED (if hard fail)
BLOCKED → OVERRIDDEN
DEPLOYED → CLOSED

---

## 22.2 Override Lifecycle

States:

* INIT
* TIMER_ACTIVE
* JUSTIFICATION_INPUT
* VALIDATED
* EXECUTED
* FLAGGED (async AI)

---

# 23. SEQUENCE FLOWS

## 23.1 Standard Trade

User → UI → API (/score)
API → Cache → return score
User clicks Deploy
API → /trade → DB insert

---

## 23.2 Override Flow

User clicks Override
UI triggers timer
User inputs justification
Frontend validates (heuristic)
API → /override
Trade executed
Async worker → AI audit

